## Java 26 Feature Glossary

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `record` | Immutable data carrier with auto-generated accessors, equals, hashCode, toString |
| `sealed` | Restricts which classes may extend or implement a type |
| `pattern matching` | Switch expressions and instanceof that bind matched values to variables |
| Virtual Threads | Lightweight threads managed by the JVM, enabling high-throughput I/O |
| Structured Concurrency | Treats related virtual threads as a single unit of work |

